en:energy-free-label-claim-but-energy-ab.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is energy free may only be made where the product does not contain more than 4 kcal or 17 kJ /100 ml. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:ca: El valor energètic en kJ ha de ser aproximadament 4‚2  vegades més gran que el valor en kcal. Els valors semblen invertits.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:cs: Hodnota energie v kJ by měla být přibližně 4‚2 krát větší než hodnota v kcal. Zdá se, že hodnoty jsou obrácené.

en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:de: Der Energiewert in kJ muss etwa 4‚2 -mal größer sein als der Wert in kcal. Die Werte scheinen vertauscht zu sein.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:el: Η ενεργειακή αξία σε kJ πρέπει να είναι περίπου 4‚2  φορές μεγαλύτερη από την τιμή σε kcal. Οι τιμές φαίνεται να είναι αντίστροφες.

en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:es: El valor energético en kJ debe ser aproximadamente 4.2 veces mayor que el valor en kcal. Los valores parecen estar invertidos.

en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:fr: La valeur de l'énergie en kJ doit être environ 4‚2  fois plus grande que la valeur en kcal. Les valeurs semblent être inversées.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:hr: Vrijednost energije u kJ mora biti oko 4‚2  puta veća od vrijednosti u kcal. Čini se da su vrijednosti obrnute.

en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:it: Il valore energetico in kJ deve essere circa 4‚2  volte maggiore del valore in kcal. I valori sembrano essere invertiti.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:ja: kJのエネルギー値はkcalの値の約4.2倍でなければなりません。値が逆になっているようです。
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:ko: kJ 단위의 에너지 값은 kcal 단위의 값보다 약 4.2배 커야 합니다. 값이 반전된 것 같습니다.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:lt: Energijos vertė kJ turi būti apie 4‚2  karto didesnė nei kcal vertė. Atrodo, kad vertės yra atvirkštinės.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:lv: Enerģijas vērtībai kJ jābūt aptuveni 4‚2  reizes lielākai nekā vērtībai kcal. Šķiet, ka vērtības ir apgrieztas.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:nl: De energiewaarde in kJ moet ongeveer 4‚2  keer groter zijn dan de waarde in kcal. De waarden lijken omgekeerd te zijn.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:no: Energiverdien i kJ må være omtrent 4‚2  ganger større enn verdien i kcal. Verdiene ser ut til å være omvendt.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:pl: Wartość energetyczna w kJ musi być około 4‚2  razy większa niż wartość w kcal. Wydaje się, że wartości są odwrócone.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:pt: O valor energético em kJ deve ser cerca de 4‚2  vezes maior que o valor em kcal. Os valores parecem estar invertidos.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:ro: Valoarea energetică în kJ trebuie să fie de aproximativ 4‚2  ori mai mare decât valoarea în kcal. Valorile par a fi inversate.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:ru: Значение энергии в кДж должно быть примерно в 4‚2  раза больше значения в ккал. Значения, кажется, перепутаны.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:sk: Hodnota energie v kJ by mala byť približne 4‚2 -krát väčšia ako hodnota v kcal. Zdá sa, že hodnoty sú obrátené.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:sl: Vrednost energije v kJ mora biti približno 4‚2 -krat večja od vrednosti v kcal. Zdi se, da so vrednosti obrnjene.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:sq: Vlera energjetike në kJ duhet të jetë rreth 4.2 herë më e madhe se vlera në kcal. Vlerat duket se janë të anasjellta.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:sr: Вредност енергије у кЈ мора бити око 4‚2  пута већа од вредности у кцал. Чини се да су вредности обрнуте.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:sv: Energivärdet i kJ måste vara cirka 4‚2  gånger större än värdet i kcal. Värdena verkar vara omvända.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:th: ค่าพลังงานในหน่วย kJ ต้องมากกว่าค่าในหน่วย kcal ประมาณ 4.2 เท่า ค่าต่างๆ ดูเหมือนจะกลับกัน
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:tr: kJ cinsinden enerji değeri, kcal cinsinden değerin yaklaşık 4‚2  katı olmalıdır. Değerler tersine çevrilmiş gibi görünüyor.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-and-kj-are-rever.description:uk: Значення енергії в кДж має бути приблизно в 4‚2  рази більшим, ніж значення в ккал. Значення, здається, переплутані.

en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:ar: قيمة الطاقة بالكيلو كالوري لا تتطابق مع القيمة المحسوبة من العناصر الغذائية الأخرى. غالبًا ما يكون ذلك بسبب خطأ في جدول الحقائق الغذائية الذي أدخله المستخدمون. في بعض الأحيان ، يكون خطأ قادمًا من المنتج.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:bg: Енергийната стойност в kcal не съвпада със стойността, изчислена от други хранителни вещества. Често това се дължи на грешка в таблицата с хранителни стойности, въведена от потребителите. Понякога това е грешка, идваща от производителя.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:ca: El valor energètic en kcal no coincideix amb el valor calculat a partir d'altres nutrients. Sovint es deu a un error a la taula de dades nutricionals introduïda pels usuaris. De vegades, és un error del productor.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:cs: Energetická hodnota v kcal neodpovídá hodnotě vypočtené z ostatních živin. Často je to způsobeno chybou v tabulce nutričních hodnot zadané uživateli. Někdy je to chyba pocházející od výrobce.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:da: Energiværdien i kcal stemmer ikke overens med værdien beregnet ud fra andre næringsstoffer. Det skyldes ofte en fejl i næringsfaktatabellen, der er indtastet af brugerne. Nogle gange er det en fejl fra producenten.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:de: Der Energiegehalt in kcal stimmt nicht mit dem aus anderen Nährstoffen berechneten Wert überein. Dies liegt häufig an einem Fehler in der von den Nutzern eingegebenen Nährwerttabelle. Manchmal ist es ein Fehler des Herstellers.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:el: Η ενεργειακή αξία σε kcal δεν ταιριάζει με την τιμή που υπολογίζεται από άλλα θρεπτικά συστατικά. Συχνά οφείλεται σε σφάλμα στον πίνακα διατροφικών στοιχείων που εισάγεται από τους χρήστες. Μερικές φορές, είναι ένα σφάλμα που προέρχεται από τον παραγωγό.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:en: The energy value in kcal does not match value computed from other nutrients. It is often due to an error in the nutrition facts table entered by the users. Sometimes, it's an error coming from the producer.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:es: El valor energético en kcal no coincide con el valor calculado a partir de otros nutrientes. A menudo se debe a un error en la tabla de datos nutricionales introducida por los usuarios. A veces, es un error del productor.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:fi: Energia-arvo kcal ei vastaa muiden ravintoaineiden perusteella laskettua arvoa. Tämä johtuu usein käyttäjien syöttämän ravintosisältötaulukon virheestä. Joskus se on tuottajan virhe.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:fr: La valeur énergétique entrée en kcal ne correspond pas à la valeur calculée à partir des autres nutriments. C'est souvent dû à une erreur dans le tableau nutritionel complété par les utilisateurs. Parfois il s'agit d'une erreur sur le packaging.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:hr: Energetska vrijednost u kcal ne odgovara vrijednosti izračunatoj iz drugih hranjivih tvari. To je često zbog pogreške u tablici nutritivnih vrijednosti koju su unijeli korisnici. Ponekad je to pogreška proizvođača.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:hu: A kcal-ban megadott energiaérték nem egyezik a többi tápanyagból számított értékkel. Ez gyakran a felhasználók által megadott táplálkozási táblázat hibájából adódik. Néha a gyártótól származó hiba.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:it: Il valore energetico in kcal non corrisponde al valore calcolato dagli altri nutrienti. Spesso è dovuto a un errore nella tabella dei valori nutrizionali inserita dagli utenti. A volte è un errore proveniente dal produttore.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:ja: kcalのエネルギー値が、他の栄養素から計算された値と一致しません。多くの場合、ユーザーが入力した栄養成分表示の表に誤りがあることが原因です。生産者からのエラーである場合もあります。
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:ko: kcal의 에너지 값이 다른 영양소로부터 계산된 값과 일치하지 않습니다. 이는 종종 사용자가 입력한 영양 성분표의 오류 때문입니다. 때로는 생산자의 오류이기도 합니다.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:nl: De energiewaarde in kcal komt niet overeen met de waarde die is berekend op basis van andere voedingsstoffen. Dit komt vaak door een fout in de voedingswaardetabel die door de gebruikers is ingevoerd. Soms is het een fout van de producent.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:pl: Wartość energetyczna w kcal nie odpowiada wartości obliczonej na podstawie innych składników odżywczych. Często wynika to z błędu w tabeli wartości odżywczych wprowadzonej przez użytkowników. Czasami jest to błąd pochodzący od producenta.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:pt: O valor energético em kcal não corresponde ao valor calculado a partir de outros nutrientes. Muitas vezes, isso ocorre devido a um erro na tabela de informações nutricionais inserida pelos usuários. Às vezes, é um erro do produtor.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:ru: Значение энергии в ккал не соответствует значению, вычисленному на основе других питательных веществ. Часто это связано с ошибкой в таблице пищевой ценности, введенной пользователями. Иногда это ошибка, допущенная производителем.
en:energy-value-in-kcal-does-not-match-v.description:zh: 千卡能量值与从其他营养素计算出的值不匹配。 这通常是由于用户输入的营养成分表中的错误造成的。 有时，这是生产商造成的错误。

en:energy-value-in-kj-does-not-match-val.description:fr: La valeur de l'énergie en kJ doit être environ 4‚2  fois plus grande que la valeur en kcal. Les valeurs semblent être inversées.

en:environmental-score-origins-of-ingred.description:en: Origins of ingredients are one of the Environmental Score components. They are currently extracted from the ingredient list and the Origins field.

en:environmental-score-packaging-packagi.description:en: No packaging data - Packaging is one of the components of the Environmental Score, and thus it's important to have packaging data.

en:environmental-score-quality-warnings.description:en: Data quality warnings that might affect Environmental Score computation

en:fibers-warnings.description:en: There might be an issue with the fibers nutrient

en:gs1-coupon-common-currency-area-prefi.description:en: This product has a barcode with a GS1 coupon common currency area prefix. This is likely a food data quality error as it indicates that the barcode is associated with a coupon rather than a food product.

en:gs1-coupon-prefix.description:en: This product has a barcode which has the format of a GS1 coupon prefix. This is probably a test by someone who scanned a coupon barcode, and added it to Open Food Facts.

en:gs1-future-coupon-prefix.description:en: This product has a barcode with a GS1 future coupon prefix. This is likely a food data quality error as it indicates that the barcode is associated with a coupon that is not yet valid or has expired, rather than a food product.

en:gs1-isbn-prefix.description:en: The International Standard Book Number -ISBN- is for books. In other terms, this is not food, and this should be moved to Open Products Facts by inputting OPF in the Categories field.

en:gs1-issn-prefix.description:en: The International Standard Serial Number -ISSN- is for serial publications. In other terms, this is not food, and this should be moved to Open Products Facts by inputting OPF in the Categories field.

en:gs1-refund-prefix.description:en: This product has a barcode with a GS1 refund prefix. This is likely a food data quality error as it indicates that the barcode is associated with a refund rather than a food product.

en:gs1-warnings.description:en: Data quality warnings linked to GS1 format -producers imports-

en:high-fibres-label-claim-but-fibre-bel.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is high in fibre may only be made where the product contains at least 6 g of fibre per 100 g or at least 3 g of fibre per 100 kcal. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:high-in-biotin-label-claim-but-biotin.description:en: In EU, claim that a food is a source of vitamins and/or minerals may only be made where the product contains at least a significant amount as defined in the Annex to Directive 90/496/EEC. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32024L1438

en:high-in-calcium-label-claim-but-calci.description:en: In EU, claim that a food is a source of vitamins and/or minerals may only be made where the product contains at least a significant amount as defined in the Annex to Directive 90/496/EEC. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32024L1438

en:high-in-iodine-label-claim-but-iodine.description:en: In EU, claim that a food is a source of vitamins and/or minerals may only be made where the product contains at least a significant amount as defined in the Annex to Directive 90/496/EEC. en:iodine-source-label-claim-but-iodine-.description:en: In EU, claim that a food is a source of vitamins and/or minerals may only be made where the product contains at least a significant amount as defined in the Annex to Directive 90/496/EEC. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32024L1438

en:iron-source-label-claim-but-iron-belo.description:en: In EU, claim that a food is a source of vitamins and/or minerals may only be made where the product contains at least a significant amount as defined in the Annex to Directive 90/496/EEC. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32024L1438

en:low-energy-label-claim-but-energy-abo.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is low in energy may only be made where the product does not contain more than 40 kcal or 170 kJ /100 g for solids or more than 20 kcal or 80 kJ /100 ml for liquids. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:low-fat-label-claim-but-fat-above-lim.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is low fat may only be made where the product contains no more than 3 g of fat per 100 g for solids or 1‚5 g of fat per 100 ml for liquids. 1‚8 g of fat per 100 ml for semi-skimmed milk. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:low-saturated-fat-label-claim-but-fat.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is fat free may only be made if the sum of saturated fatty acids and trans-fatty acids in the product does not exceed 1‚5 g per 100 g for solids or 0‚75 g/100 ml for liquids and in either case the sum of saturated fatty acids and trans-fatty acids must not provide more than 10 % of energy. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:low-sodium-or-low-salt-label-claim-bu.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is low sodium or low salt may only be made where the product contains no more than 0‚12 g of sodium, or the equivalent value for salt, per 100 g or per 100 ml. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:low-sugar-label-claim-but-sugar-above.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is low sugar may only be made where the product contains no more than 5 g of sugars per 100 g for solids or 2‚5 g of sugars per 100 ml for liquids. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:magnesium-source-label-claim-but-magn.description:en: In EU, claim that a food is a source of vitamins and/or minerals may only be made where the product contains at least a significant amount as defined in the Annex to Directive 90/496/EEC. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A32024L1438

en:no-added-sodium-or-no-added-salt-labe.description:en: In EU, a claim that sodium/salt has not been added to a food may only be made where the product does not contain any added sodium/salt or any other ingredient containing added sodium/salt and the product contains no more than 0‚12 g sodium, or the equivalent value for salt, per 100 g or 100 ml. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:no-added-sugar-label-claim-but-contai.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is with no added sugars may only be made where the product does not contain any added mono- or disaccharides or any other food used for its sweetening properties. If sugars are naturally present in the food, the following indication should also appear on the label: ‘CONTAINS NATURALLY OCCURRING SUGARS'. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213

en:no-fat-label-claim-but-fat-above-0-5.description:en: In EU, a claim that a food is fat free may only be made where the product contains no more than 0‚5 g of fat per 100 g or 100 ml. See: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX%3A02006R1924-20141213
